debconf-translation-manager (0.7.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Complete rewrite with workflow-based NavigationView UI
  * PackageListPage: sortable, searchable, color-coded untranslated packages
  * PackageDetailPage: download PO, translate, lint, submit actions
  * PoEditorPage: side-by-side msgid/msgstr, fuzzy highlighting
  * SubmitDialog: one-click email with standard Debian l10n format
  * StatsPage: SQLite history, language rankings, CSV export
  * Settings: language, SMTP, Gmail preset
  * Swedish translation 100%

